(329, 'Stephen Collins', 'scfirsteditionbooks@hotmail.com', '0882302158', '4 Pickering Avenue', 'FULLARTON', 'SA', '5063', 'Australia', '2009-07-08', '2009-07-17', 9, 4, 0, 'None Specified', '', 'Stephen R Collins', '377850081553144', 'Amex', '10', '07', 9633, 0, 'Mark\r\n\r\nThanks for your help, as agreed weekly rate to apply, i.e. $360 per night thus $3240 for 9 nights.  As we will be celebrating my 50th any apartment with a really good view would be really appreciated...!  look forward to seeing you in July.\r\n\r\nThanks\r\n\r\nStephen and Sue Collins', '2008-12-17 22:27:04', '58.170.93.73', 'Processed', 1, 'Dear Stephen Collins,\r\n\r\nThank you for your booking. This email is to let you know that your booking has been confirmed as the agreed weekly rate of $360 per night thus $3240 for 9 nights. \r\n\r\n3x bedroom harbour view apartment\r\nArrival 2009-07-08 \r\nDeparture 2009-07-17 \r\n\r\nPlease forward a mastercard or visa card details so we can place a one night''s accommodation + 1.5% credit card fee deposit to make this reservation.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to you celebrating your 50th with us.\r\n\r\nBest regards\r\n\r\nMark', 'HS $420 / LS $380', '', ''),
